{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 dda_CURATE \u8211- Instant sound curation for Reaper.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 dda_CURATE is a set of Reaper scripts to help you rate, organize, and categorize your sounds quickly and easily.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Rate your sounds using a color-coding system to quickly determine which ones you prefer and organize them together\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Easily move sounds to child tracks to keep similar sounds together\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Add unique description metadata to individual sounds as well as project metadata to all sounds in your collection\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Reorder your sounds based on different variables including item length or rating to keep your project neat and tidy\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Printout all project sound information in one easy-to-read, easy-to-copy-paste window\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab And more!\sa180\par}
